      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRAVE ANNIE (1) is a well performed dog and winner of 12 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at this track (22.72). Has a good record here at this journey. Yet to miss the placings in four runs from this box, including two wins. Has ability and looks hard to stop. JIMMY'S JET (4) is worth forgiving last start after finishing fifth (22.52) at this track over 400m. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won 11 of 18 tries. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Cannot be taken lightly. RAMBO'S SHOUT (8) is a smart beginner who has shown good improvement at his last two starts, breaking through last time at this track over 488m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expecting another bold showing. LITTLE WILDFIRE (2) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 3.5 lengths away in third (22.84). Overdue and gets his chance.",
